# Market Intelligence Engine — Full Upgrade Plan

> **Goal:** Make MIYAR's market data comprehensive, always up-to-date, and self-correcting — covering prices, trends, designs, and developer projects.

## Current State (What Already Works)

| Layer | Status | Detail |
|-------|--------|--------|
| 23 Connectors | ✅ | 22 HTML + 1 PDF (SCAD) |
| [DynamicConnector](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/ingestion/connectors/dynamic.ts#235-538) | ✅ | 4 prompt types: pricing, developer, market research, government |
| Orchestrator | ✅ | Parallel (max 3), duplicate detection (sourceUrl + itemName + captureDate) |
| Scheduler | ✅ | Per-source cron via `source_registry.scrapeSchedule` |
| Firecrawl SDK | ✅ | Used for JS-rendered sources (Bayut, PropertyFinder) |
| Freshness | ✅ | green/amber/red badges + weight multipliers |
| Source Registry | ✅ | DB-driven, 54+ columns, supports dynamic connectors |

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]  
> This is a large upgrade with 8 modules across 3 phases. I recommend implementing **Phase 1 first** (upsert + quality + freshness) since these fix fundamental data integrity issues. Phases 2 and 3 add new intelligence capabilities. Please confirm the priority order.

> [!WARNING]  
> The Source Discovery Engine (Module B) will use Firecrawl search + Gemini to find new websites automatically. This needs the `FIRECRAWL_API_KEY` env var set. Please confirm you have an active Firecrawl plan with search credits.

---

## Phase 1 — Data Integrity (Modules A, E, D)

### Module A: Upsert Engine

**Problem:** Orchestrator currently does insert-or-skip. Same item, new price → skipped as duplicate.  
**Solution:** Change to insert-or-update. When match found, update price fields + log a `price_change_event`.

#### [MODIFY] [orchestrator.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/ingestion/orchestrator.ts)

Replace [isDuplicate()](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/ingestion/orchestrator.ts#99-126) with `upsertEvidence()`:

```diff
-// If duplicate, skip
-if (await isDuplicate(sourceUrl, itemName, captureDate)) {
-  skipped++;
-  continue;
-}
-// Insert new record
-await db.insert(evidenceRecords).values(record);
+// Upsert: find existing record by sourceUrl + itemName
+const existing = await findExistingRecord(sourceUrl, itemName);
+if (existing) {
+  // Update prices + captureDate, log price change
+  await updateExistingRecord(existing, record);
+  updated++;
+} else {
+  await db.insert(evidenceRecords).values(record);
+  created++;
+}
```

Key functions to add:
- `findExistingRecord(sourceUrl, itemName)` — Find by source + item (ignoring date)
- `updateExistingRecord(existing, newData)` — Update price fields, bump `captureDate`, create `price_change_event` if delta > 2%
- `logPriceChange(existing, newData)` — Insert into `price_change_events` table when price changes significantly

Report fields to update: `evidenceUpdated` count alongside `evidenceCreated` and `evidenceSkipped`.

